<span class="pl-c"><span class="pl-c">#</span>## 可选配置，如果 type 为 `discussions2` 类型，才需要以下配置</span>
<span class="pl-c"><span class="pl-c">#</span> type: `issues` | `discussions` | `discussions2`, default is `discussions`</span>
<span class="pl-ent">type</span>: <span class="pl-s">discussions2</span>
